<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٨)</span> بابٌ: هَلْ يَبِيعُ حاضِرٌ لِبادٍ بِغَيْرِ أَجْرٍ؟ وَهَلْ يُعِينُهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَوْ يَنْصَحُهُ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذا اسْتَنْصَحَ أَحَدُكُمْ أَخاهُ فَلْيَنْصَحْ لَهُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَرَخَّصَ فِيهِ عَطاءٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>